### Hadith 4:9

*Narrated Anas:*

A Jew crushed the head of a girl between two stones. She was asked, "Who
has done so to you, so-and-so? So-and-so?" Till the name of the Jew was
mentioned, whereupon she nodded (in agreement). So the Jew was brought
and was questioned till he confessed. The Prophet then ordered that his
head be crushed with stones.

